@inherits AppComponentBase
@page "/"

<section class="page-sec to-the-moon-sec">
    <div class="sec-content">
        <div class="sec-title">To the Moon</div>
        <div class="sec-subtitle">through the Clouds.</div>
        <div class="sec-desc">Bit is a digital innovation company with software development at its core. We help out our customers innovate with designing and building their digital products efficiently with our Agile mindset and lean processes.</div>
        <a class="sec-btn--primary" href="/cases">See Our Showcases</a>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-bg"></div>
</section>

<section class="page-sec projects-sec">
    <div class="title-container--primary">
        <div class="title--primary">Our </div>
        <div class="title--primary">Projects<span class="title-border--primary"></span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-subtitle">Your story will go up there</div>
    <BitCarousel InfiniteSliding="true" Style="width:500px">
        @foreach (var showCase in Cases)
        {
            <BitCarouselItem>
                <div class="slide-photo" style="background-image: url(@($"/images/home/slide.svg"))"></div>
                <div class="slide-content">
                    <div class="slide-title">@showCase.Name</div>
                    <div class="slide-desc">@showCase.Description</div>
                </div>
            </BitCarouselItem>
        }
    </BitCarousel>
    <a class="sec-btn--primary" href="/cases">See Our Showcases</a>
</section>

<section class="page-sec services-sec">
    <div class="title-container--primary">
        <div class="title--primary">Our </div>
        <div class="title--primary">Services<span class="title-border--primary"></span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-desc">Bit provides a wide range of services. you find everything you need here. We build prototypes and test your products to make sure they are perfect.</div>
    <div class="sec-card-group">
        <div class="service-card web-development-card">
            Web development
            <div class="service-card-overlay">
                <div class="service-card-title">Web development</div>
                <div class="service-card-desc">We offer custom web development services to ensure your website is tailored to your unique business needs, responsive across all devices, and visually stunning. Let us help you build a website that truly reflects the unique nature of your business.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card app-development-card">
            App development
            <div class="service-card-overlay">
                <div class="service-card-title">App development</div>
                <div class="service-card-desc">Bit's team of experts provides exceptional mobile app development services, so you don't have to look elsewhere. Let us help bring your vision to life and deliver a smooth user experience for your mobile audience.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card mobile-development-card">
            Mobile development
            <div class="service-card-overlay">
                <div class="service-card-title">Mobile development</div>
                <div class="service-card-desc">Bit's team of experts provides exceptional mobile app development services, so you don't have to look elsewhere. Let us help bring your vision to life and deliver a smooth user experience for your mobile audience.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card ai-card">
            Artificial intelligence
            <div class="service-card-overlay">
                <div class="service-card-title">Artificial intelligence</div>
                <div class="service-card-desc">AI made everything easier and more efficient. With Bit, you can have it on-board too. Remote device management, wireless connectivity and smart monitoring can be run through artificial intelligence more easily. </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card design-card">
            UI/ UX design
            <div class="service-card-overlay">
                <div class="service-card-title">UI/ UX design</div>
                <div class="service-card-desc">Our team of UI/UX experts creates unique, aesthetically pleasing and functional websites, applications and webpages that accurately reflect your business, ensuring an outstanding user experience for your clients and users.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card support-card">
            Technical support
            <div class="service-card-overlay">
                <div class="service-card-title">Technical support</div>
                <div class="service-card-desc">Free up your time by entrusting our support service to handle any operational issues, allowing you to focus on expanding your business.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card cloud-card">
            Cloud base solutions
            <div class="service-card-overlay">
                <div class="service-card-title">cloud base solutions</div>
                <div class="service-card-desc">Unlock the full potential of your business with our high-performance cloud solutions. Unlike traditional options, cloud solutions offer limitless scalability and speed. Bit offers cutting-edge technology to ensure that your business is both agile and efficient.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card game-development-card">
            Game development
            <div class="service-card-overlay">
                <div class="service-card-title">Game development</div>
                <div class="service-card-desc">Let Bit bring your game vision to life with our expert team of 2D and 3D game developers. Experience captivating and engaging gameplay with our industry-leading expertise.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="sec-btn--primary" href="/services">Services</a>
</section>

<section class="page-sec process-sec">
    <div class="title-container--primary">
        <div class="title--primary">Our </div>
        <div class="title--primary">Process<span class="title-border--primary"></span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-desc">Our process begins with creating a comprehensive roadmap for your business. We then work closely with you to bring your ideas to fruition by building a polished prototype that perfectly aligns with your vision and exceeds your expectations.</div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-1">
        <div class="process-card-title">Functional Specification</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">This is the initial step in the development process where the goals and requirements of the project are defined and a map is created to guide the development process.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-2">
        <div class="process-card-title">Prototyping</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">This stage involves creating a prototype or demo of the product to be developed. Feedback is gathered at this stage and changes are made as needed.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-3">
        <div class="process-card-title">Setting Up Your Team</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">A dedicated, talented, and exclusive team is set up for the project. The team composition can be chosen based on budget and deadlines are established.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-4">
        <div class="process-card-title">Agile Software Development</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">This approach is used to speed up the development process, ensuring that the product is sustainable, well-designed, and delivered quickly.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-5">
        <div class="process-card-title">Technical And Marketing Support</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">After launch, services such as SEO, marketing, performance monitoring, and upgrades are provided to ensure the success of the product in the market.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="page-sec team-sec">
    <div class="title-container--primary">
        <div class="title--primary">Who </div>
        <div class="title--primary">We Are?<span class="title-border--primary"></span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-content-container">
        <div class="sec-content">
            <div class="sec-title">DoorDash / Food delivey app</div>
            <div class="sec-desc">Bit  is a full-service software developing agency. Our job is to make your dream business come true. We have combined quality with performance and made a new standard out of it. Bit gathered talents so you don't need to look for them elsewhere. We help you to build your website, your application, UI/UX and your future. It's a new world and new worlds need robust solutions.</div>
            <a class="sec-btn--primary" href="/about">Meet Our Team</a>
        </div>
        <div class="team-photo"></div>
    </div>
</section>